<title>IS MY NAME WRITTEN THERE?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa sum ka ngaitam hi,
 Sana leh dangka tawh;
 Van gam thu ngaihtuoh ing ka,
 A huong sung ka lut na'ng;
 Na Lalgam lehkhabu-ah,
 A pek hawih tak achun;
 Lalpa Isu, ei hilh in,
 Ka min chuh a chuong tam?

[V2]
 Ka min chuh a chuong tam?
 A pek vam hawih chungah?
 Na Lalgam lehkhabu-ah,
 Ka min chuh a chuong ta'm?

[V3]
 2. Lalpa, ka gitloh a tam,
 Luipi pilnel bangin;
 Mahleh Lalpa, Na thisan,
 Kei a din a hun hi;
 Na thutiem zik ahi a
 Lehkha mal hawih tak chun,
 &quot;Na gitlohna san mahleh,
 Vuk bang vam sak ka&quot; tin.

[V4]
 3. Aw, zie khawpi hawihtak a,
 In vak lopitak chuh;
 A sungah hukdam chate'n,
 Puon vam, thieng a silh ui;
 Gitlohna um ta puona,
 Thilpha hihbuok dingin;
 Angel ven khawpi achun,
 Ka min chuh a chuong tai.

[V5]
 Ka min chuh a chuong tai,
 A pek vam hawih chungah;
 Na Lalgam lehkhabu-ah,
 Ka min chuh a chuong tai.</lyrics>
</song>